International Summary

As of Saturday, July 4, 2020, the total number of confirmed cases worldwide is 12,600,000.

The total number of deaths is 664,000.

The number of reported recoveries is 6,840,000.

The overall mortality rate based on reported deaths and confirmed cases is 5%.
